Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我什么都没听懂\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't understand any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么别墅  在哪\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What villa? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真是不可思议到让人无言以对\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This is too extraordinary for any words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是叫鸽子别墅  在土伦附近\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's called La Villa des Colombes, and it's near Toulon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但为什么会属于您\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But why was it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而且您怎么从没提过\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And why have you never said anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为我以为那是个玩笑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Because I thought it was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}从头说起吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Start at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}多年前  你出生之前  我去了趟法国\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Years ago, before you were born, I was in France,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}遇到了一个男人  蒙米拉侯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I met a man, the Marquis de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他邀请我去他刚买的一栋别墅做客几日\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And he invited me to spend some time at a villa he'd just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大概一年多后  他写信给我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A year or so later, he wrote to me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说他已把别墅转到了我名下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and said he'd transferred the villa into my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我根本没想到他是认真的  我没在意\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I never thought he was serious, so I didn't pay any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-但并不是玩笑话吗  -看来不是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- But it wasn't a joke? - It seems not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他最近过世了  让他的遗孀惊讶的是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He died recently, and to his widow's alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们多年来每年冬天都去住的别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}the villa they've been using every winter for years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}居然是在老夫人名下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}was registered to Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他一直没改过\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He never changed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我需要几个签名  -好的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Now, I'll need some signatures. - Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您为什么要送给茜玻\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why have you given it to Sybbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的孩子在这里有财产可继承\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Your children are well set up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}伊迪丝的孩子更是不愁了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and Edith's are more than taken care of,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但布朗普顿会由汤姆和露西的孩子继承\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but Brompton will go to a child of Tom and Lucy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这样亲爱的茜玻的独女就继承不到什么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So darling Sybil's only daughter will inherit little,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想改变这一点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I wanted to correct that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这个蒙米拉有多少家人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What family did he have, uh, this M-Montmirail chap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}遗孀和一个儿子  也就是现任侯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The widow and a son, the present marquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那位母亲很想把此事闹上法庭\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The mother is keen they should take the matter to court.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-这也难怪  -怎么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Well, you can't blame her. - Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果她丈夫想把房子送给我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If her husband wanted me to have the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们凭什么说不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}who are we to argue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您就没想过要拒绝吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You never thought to turn it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你看我像是会拒绝一栋南法别墅的人吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Do I look as if I'd turn down a villa in the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫里先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Murray?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-可以帮我个忙吗  -请讲\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- May I ask a favor? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我有个任务交给你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I have a task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}信里都说明了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's all explained in this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我过几日再发电报  以防还有什么问题\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll telephone in a few days in case there are questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好的  格兰瑟姆夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Of course, Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我要赶不上车了  -再见  莫里先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Now, I hear my train calling. - Goodbye, Mr. Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们想让我说出他为什么这么干\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You want me to tell you why he did it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但其实\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}when the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也不知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那我就此道晚安了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And with that, I will say good night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们议论我的神秘过往去吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and leave you to discuss my mysterious past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}丹可  别推推拉拉的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, Denker, don't steer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我又不是赛车\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not a racing car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真可惜了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}More's the pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你说什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你真得...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You really must try...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是挺奇怪的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It does seem odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们60多年前在一个度假山庄一起待了几日\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They spend a few days together in the same resort more than 60 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他就送了她栋房子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and he gives her a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他应该不会只是个疯子吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose he wasn't just a lunatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们会想证明他是疯了的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, that's what they'll try to prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得奶奶这样照顾茜玻真是太好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I think it's marvelous of Granny to take care of Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}哪怕蒙米拉先生真是疯了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Even if Monsieur de Montmirail was as mad as a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但妈妈为什么从没提起过呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But why did Mama never say a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在她看来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}As far as she's concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她半个多世纪前收到了一封古怪的信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}she received a very eccentric letter more than half a century ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当时以为只是胡闹\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}she considered it potty at the time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.20,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就再没去想过这事了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and never gave it another thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好样的  玛丽戈德\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well done, Marigold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很好  打得好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's right. Good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}退后\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}保姆  看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nanny, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有电话找您  老爷\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A telephone call for you, milord.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-是谁  -一位巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Who is it? - Uh, a Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-说是英国雄狮的  -那是什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Says he's from British Lion. - What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不是一家电影公司吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a film company, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我最好去看看是怎么回事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I better find out what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们夏季打算怎么处置别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What will they do with the villa in the summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}又不能租出去  没人那时候去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They can't let it. Nobody goes there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-现在有人去了  -难道不热吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Oh, they do now. - Well, surely it's too hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看来是不热\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-妈妈  -你好  亲爱的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Mummy! - Hello, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈  来玩吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mummy, come and play!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在比赛呢  来  快\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a race. Come on. Quickly.
