Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您是说他想在唐顿拍电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You mean he wants to make a film at Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您怎么说的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我委婉地拒绝了  -那我再打回去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- I let him down gently. - Then I'll ring him back.
