Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有什么意义\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}肯定会给钱吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I suppose there'd be a fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亨利什么时候回家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When does Henry get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}赶不上这事了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not in time for this.
