Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有他你也能行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You can manage it without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗  那么就都靠我了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I see. So it's down to me, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不能指望我们去应付演艺人士\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You can't expect us to deal with kinema people.
