Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}钱总能派上用场\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The money would be useful, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你跟亨利一切都好吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is everything all right with Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他爱车\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's in love with cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他爱速度  他爱冒险\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's in love with speed. He's in love with adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他好像还爱我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's also in love with me, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我似乎无法抵消另外三样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I don't seem to cancel out the other three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你本以为你能吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And you thought you would?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大概是吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}准备好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}太合适了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}直到不久前  电影拍摄还主要在摄影棚内\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Until recently, filmmaking was largely confined to the studios,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但现在这一过程有所发展\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but now the process has opened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}阿贝尔·冈斯去年的《拿破仑》\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Abel Gance's Napoléon last year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}展现了摄影机在外景地的前景\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}showed what a camera can do on location,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在真实的房子  场地拍摄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}filming in real houses, real landscapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是部什么样的电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What sort of film is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}《赌徒》背景设在1875年\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The Gambler is set in 1875.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一位伯爵的女儿  安·厄斯金小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}An earl's daughter, Lady Anne Erskine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}爱上了一个男人  结果此人是个赌徒\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}falls in love with a man who turns out to be a gambler,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这让她的家人十分惊恐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to her family's horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不难想象\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们在乡下的一场别墅宴会上结识\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They meet at a house party in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很快情况就一发不可收拾\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and things soon spin out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们还去了一间很时髦的赌场\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There are visits to a smart gambling club,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们就在这里拍\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}which we'd do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在唐顿开赌场吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A gambling club at Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这非要了奶奶的命\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That would finish Granny off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有爸爸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And Papa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我们需要时间考虑  -当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- We must have time to think. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是我的名片\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Here's my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有任何问题就联系我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ring me if you have any questions at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我会叫巴罗来送你出去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll get Barrow to see you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们有两个问题需要先问清\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose there are two questions that we would need the answer to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}才能真正开始讨论\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}before we can really have the discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们会待一个月左右\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'd be here for about a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}把名片翻过来  我写了我们的出价\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and if you turn the card over, you'll see what we'd pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当然  这还是可以商量的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Of course, that's negotiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-再见  巴伯先生  -再见\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Goodbye, Mr. Barber. - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这还只是起价吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And that's the starting point?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.23,0:12:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这主意糟透了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think it's a horrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}浓妆艳抹的女演员和醉醺醺的男演员\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Actresses plastered in makeup and actors just plastered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}粗手粗脚地动我们的东西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}scrambling over our things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们得时刻注意餐具室丢没丢勺子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'd have to keep counting the spoons in the pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}本地人可能不会高兴\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The locals might take a dim view.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可别为此就放弃\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, you mustn't let that stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}郡民们看什么都不高兴\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The county takes a dim view of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你得考虑费用的事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You have to consider the fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们不需要谈钱的事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We don't need to talk about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但您得考虑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But you need to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别的不说  您可以重修屋顶了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You could have a new roof, for a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}再不修要发大水了  那可如何是好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You could soon be looking at real flooding, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果您拒绝\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you turn them down,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们能不能说服他们北上去布兰克斯特堡呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}do you think we could persuade them to drive further north to Brancaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈  您怎么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mama, where do you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}玛丽  亲爱的  你可以带你父亲去阁楼看看吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mary, dear, will you take your father to see the attics?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看他是好久没上去过了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't think he's been there for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我都好些年没上来过了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I haven't been up here for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们面临的就是这样的情况\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, this is the situation we're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.53,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有了钱  我们就能把房子修缮好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}With the money, we can bring the house up to snuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}以匹配我们对庄园的投入\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to match what we've spent on the estate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}也能抬头挺胸地迈入30年代\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and enter the 1930s with our heads held high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-但如果您不愿意...  -不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- But if you don't want to... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不  你掌舵向前吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No, you steer ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你现在是船长了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're the captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这我是知道的  哪怕你以为我不知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I am aware of that, even if you think I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还得我去把消息告诉卡森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And now I have the unenviable task
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这可不是什么美差\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}of breaking the news to Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真难以置信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在这里拍电影  他们能这么做吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}To make a film here? Can they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}会有电影明星来吗  著名影星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Would there be film stars? Famous ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}给她点水吧  免得她晕过去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, give her some water before she passes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}事情还没定下呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nothing's decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你倒是可以激动\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's all very fine to get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}反正你住在农场\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You live at the farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们其余的人时时刻刻\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The rest of us will have them in and out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}都要看着他们进进出出\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and round about every hour God sends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而且老夫人怎么办\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And what of Her Ladyship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只想要安度晚年\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Hoping for a peaceful end...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}却突然被丢进了一个杂牌马戏团\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}...and suddenly plunged into a three-ring circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我赞同黛西的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I agree with Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们有机会认识\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'll get to know men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只在大银幕上见过的男女\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}we've only seen upon the silver screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-如果这对房子有好处  -这就是重点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- And if it's good for the house... - This is the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果有钱流入或许会至关重要\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}An injection of cash could make all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们提到数了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They mention how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}即便提了也与我们无关\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's not our business if they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-他们没说  -再见了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- They did not. - Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-再见  -再见\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}再见  休斯太太\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Good night, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不论如何  时代在变  我们也得跟上脚步\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Still, times change and we must change with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}帕克太太  我们也该回家了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mrs. Parker. We should be getting home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好啊  帕克先生  我这就走\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Very good, Mr. Parker. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}黛西对他可比对我听话多了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Daisy's more obedient with him than she ever was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许他让她更开心\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maybe he makes her happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也尽力了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I did me best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A moving picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在唐顿拍摄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}At Downton?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道这不可思议\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know it sounds unlikely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但也没那么可怕吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I'm not sure it's quite as awful as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么没有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}粗鲁粗俗的演员\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Rough and vulgar actors and actresses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在各个房间里走动  手脚还不干净\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}strolling through the rooms with their sticky fingers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}坐在英国国王曾用餐的桌子旁的椅子里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}sitting on the chairs, eating at the table where the King of England once sat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}简直跟法国大革命最糟的情况有的一拼了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, this smacks of the worst excesses of the French Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那我们要让他们不许坐下  戴上手套吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Should we ask them to stay standing and put them in gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是衰落  艾尔希\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This is a comedown, Elsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是下滑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This is a falling-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是跟暴民政治眉来眼去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They are flirting with mob rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.15,0:15:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但有钱拿  查理  他们又需要钱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But it will pay, Charlie, and they need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这么说的话  干吗不对公众开放大宅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, by that argument, why not open the place to the public
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}让他们把每个角落都看个遍\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and have them poke and pry in every corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们这么做过一次\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We tried that once,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.33,0:15:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}然后不是都决定再没有下次了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I thought we'd all decided never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你再这么下去  要犯心脏病了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You carry on like that, you'll give yourself a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果我们沦落至此  那我还不如结束痛苦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd be better off out of it if this is what we've come to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}安迪  你能把报纸折好吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Andy, I wonder if you might fold that newspaper properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要拿去楼上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll take it upstairs with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大宅要拍电影了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So, moving picture to be made at the big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那对你们会意味着什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What will that mean for the pair of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-不好说  -但肯定很让人激动\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Can't say exactly. - But it'll be exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看看电影怎么拍的  见到明星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Seeing how a film's made, meeting the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我劝你还是离他们远远的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd keep clear of them if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}远离这一切\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Keep clear of all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那我就道晚安了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll say good night, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-晚安  -晚安\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Good night. - Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说了一通还忘了拿报纸了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Forgot the paper after all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}脑子真不好使\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Memory like a sieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}晚安\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别忘了  这是他的农场  不是我们的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Remember, it's his farm, not ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是格兰瑟姆伯爵的农场  他只是佃户\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's Lord Grantham's farm, and he's only the tenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但别说什么你会后悔的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But don't say anything you'll regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}问题就在这里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我早晚会说错话  那我们怎么办\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm bound to in the end, and then where will we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫里让人把遗嘱翻译好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Murray's had the will translated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}据说  蒙米拉提到他结婚前还年轻时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Apparently, Montmirail refers to an idyllic interlude
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟妈妈曾有过一段诗意的短暂情缘\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}he spent with Mama as a young man before he was married.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫里还说了什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What else did Murray have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很奇怪\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why, it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}遗孀想抵抗遗嘱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The widow wants to fight the will,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但儿子则认为可以友好地解决\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but the son believes it can be settled in a friendly way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}要是我就拿铁丝网把别墅围起来  拿板子把窗户遮上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd cover the villa with barbed wire and board up the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他说他希望我们去一趟\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He says he'd like us to visit him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈显然无法远行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, clearly Mama can't travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他叫我们带上汤姆和露西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but he asked us to bring Tom and Lucy with us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为他得知茜玻将成为继承人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}now that he knows Sybbie is to be the beneficiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你觉得呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们有机会了解露西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, we could get to know Lucy better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果走运的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And with any luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们也能因此完全错过玛丽可怕的电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}it would mean we'd miss the whole of Mary's frightful film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我找到了  莫娜·达格利什\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I found it. Myrna Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就知道我有张她的靓照\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I knew I had a good one of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她真是美得经典\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Her beauty is so classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我有张他的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've got one of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}盖·德克斯特饰演《卡萨诺瓦》\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Guy Dexter in Casanova.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我光是想想就脸红\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The very thought of it makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他真是不一般\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There is something about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}像一只要扑上来的野兽\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Like a wild animal ready to spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}要扑倒你吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ready to spring on you, you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}够了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们不小心的话  安迪和我要吃醋了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You'll have Andy and me jealous if you don't watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那可敢情好呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真遗憾你要错过乐趣了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I hate that you'll miss all the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我都紧张了  让你单独接触盖·德克斯特\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm nervous now, leaving you alone with Guy Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么可能\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The chance would be a fine thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你觉得呢  伯蒂  -有麻烦了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- What do you think, Bertie? - A complication.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}汤姆说他们还得带上莫德·巴格肖\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Tom says they'd have to bring Maud Bagshaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她的房子整理好之前她跟他们住在一起\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's living with them until her house is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们可以一起住旅馆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We can all stay in an hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那样的话  我们可以去吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In that case, can we come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那太好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.32,0:18:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们不会碍事吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We wouldn't be in the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那么除了我  大家都去吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So everyone's going except me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也不去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我一直在考虑写一篇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've been thinking about an article
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}关于夏季去南法度假的人的文章\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}on the people who visit the south of France in the summer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你又写作了吗  太好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you writing again? I'm pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}伊迪丝每周几天会回杂志社工作\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Edith's back at the magazine for a couple of days a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}小彼得呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And little Peter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他的保姆很好  谢天谢地\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Has a wonderful nanny, thank heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你带着两个孩子  还要打理\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Can you really work with two young children
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}布兰克斯特堡  还能工作吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}while running a house like Brancaster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}过六个月再问我吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ask me in six months' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.84,0:18:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我很高兴你又开始动脑了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I'm glad to hear you're doing something with your brain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}希望她的脑子还在\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, let's hope it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我明天致电蒙米拉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll telephone Montmirail tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟他说我们会住酒店\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and explain we'll be in an hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他应该会感到如释重负\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I should think he'll be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}请进\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看到灯还亮着\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I saw the light was still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您也赞成爸爸吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose you agree with Papa
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}认为电影的事太粗俗  不值得考虑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that the whole idea of a film is too common to even be considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果能帮助唐顿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nothing is too common
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}渡过难关  那就没什么事"太粗俗"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}if it will help to keep Downton afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这样我们就有钱重修屋顶了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, we'd have enough money for a new roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只需要忍受一个月的折磨\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}At the cost of one terrible month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:18:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}老实说  我的确觉得会是折磨\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Honestly, I do think it will be pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但阁楼里用老洗脸盆接雨水的景象\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But the sight of old washbasins catching rainwater in the attics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}也让人难受\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}is terrible, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们撑过了战争  这也不在话下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We got through the war. We can get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你一定要强硬  玛丽\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But you must be firm, Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在那些人看来  我们这种女人只分两类\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}To those people, women like us fall into two categories:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}霸王和蠢货\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}dragons and fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你一定要让他们把你当霸王\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You must make sure they think of you as a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}贝茨先生和巴克斯特小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Bates and Miss Baxter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}会去照顾格兰瑟姆伯爵和夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}will go to look after Lord and Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}其他人留在唐顿  帮助摄制组\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The rest will stay at Downton to help with the film people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你别指望我帮忙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You'll get no help from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟不肯帮忙小姐不一样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In contrast to Miss Won't-Lift-a-Finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我很乐意帮忙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd love to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可以做达格利什小姐的贴身女仆吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could I be Miss Dalgleish's lady's maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我已经让安娜来做了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've asked Anna to take that on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不想扫兴  黛西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't want to be a spoilsport, Daisy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你在这里还有工作要做呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but you do have a job down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}达格利什小姐的确要在宅子里住吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We know Miss Dalgleish is staying in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的  还有导演和男主演\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She is, with the director and the leading man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.76,0:19:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}其他人会去村子里住\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The rest are going to put up in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我得去见玛丽小姐了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, I need to go and see Lady Mary.
