Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}之后便一直待在那里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I've been there ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不止我一个\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.10,0:24:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们被称为好莱坞英裔\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They call us the Hollywood Raj,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.56,0:24:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们每周会打一次板球\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and we all play cricket once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}也不会因为天气停赛了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And the weather never stops play.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你去过南法吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Do you know the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我上次去时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Last time I was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.44,0:24:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟罗纳德·科曼和格洛丽娅·斯旺森一起\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was marooned on the roof of the Negresco
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.65,0:24:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}被困在了内格莱斯科酒店的屋顶上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}with Ronald Colman and Gloria Swanson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.40,0:24:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}屋顶上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}On the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.48,0:24:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}晚饭时告诉我们故事的后半段吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You can tell us the rest of that story at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你们什么时候出发  -明天\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- When are you leaving? - Tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}从多佛去加莱  然后乘蓝色列车去尼斯\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Uh, Dover, Calais and then the Blue Train down to Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}听上去让人羡慕\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How enviable that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们导演什么时候来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When do you expect your director?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.49,0:24:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他晚饭时会来的  是吧  莫娜\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, he'll be here for dinner. Don't you think, Myrna?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.83,0:24:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我怎么知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫娜·达格利什就在这房子里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Myrna Dalgleish in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}简直不可思议\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It seems incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她爸就在老博罗市场卖水果  看她现在多发达\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Her dad sold fruit in the old Borough Market. Now look at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.84,0:24:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}成了银幕女神\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A goddess of the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.43,0:24:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你还能做她的女仆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And you're going to be her maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.39,0:24:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她带来了一堆行李\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's brought a mountain of luggage,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你和安娜不如现在过去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so I thought you and Anna could go together right now
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}帮她收拾一下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and offer to unpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}记住  你们都不了解这女人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just remember, neither of you know this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她或许并不是你们在影迷杂志上读到的那位电影明星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She may not be the film star you see in the fan magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.36,0:24:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去看看便知了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, there's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.95,0:25:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}格兰瑟姆伯爵夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}抱歉突然造访\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm sorry to burst in on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.75,0:25:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}哪里的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.63,0:25:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}其实  我立了新遗嘱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The fact is I've made a new will,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.25,0:25:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我需要你们见证我签名\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I need you both to witness my signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就是没事找事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm just fussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不过就是我的珠宝和其他一些东西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's only my jewelry and a few other pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.63,0:25:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}及时更新遗嘱一向是好事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's always a good idea to bring these things up to date.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.14,0:25:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}正好莫里也在\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Murray was down anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.26,0:25:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就想借此机会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so I thought I would take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.85,0:25:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}正好你来了  因为我想告诉你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm glad you've come, because I wanted to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.56,0:25:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}维奥莱特叫我们整理她的东西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that Violet has asked us to go through her things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.56,0:25:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么  她为什么找你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What? Why has she asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.06,0:25:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我真的不知道  不过真要有什么重要的东西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I really don't know, but, of course, anything of interest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.82,0:25:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}肯定会告诉你和罗伯特\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}will be referred to Robert and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.65,0:25:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就是觉得该告诉你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I just thought you ought to be told.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.40,0:25:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她想把后事都安排好  不用再为此烦恼\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, she wants her death to be ordered and free of bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.36,0:25:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就是维奥莱特的作风\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's all very Violet-like, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.78,0:25:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我们是不是不该去法国  -当然不会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Are we wrong to go to France? - Oh, certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.33,0:25:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}要是真有什么情况\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mary can send a telegram
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.70,0:25:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}玛丽可以发电报\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}if there are any dark developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但不会的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But there won't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.46,0:25:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不会假装我一向把她奉若神明\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't pretend I've always worshipped at her shrine,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.59,0:25:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但没了她肯定会很别扭\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but it will be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.05,0:26:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等她走了  玛丽肯定会想她的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And Mary will miss her when she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.13,0:26:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}玛丽会成为她的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mary will become her,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.97,0:26:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她就后继有人了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so the gap will be filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.30,0:26:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我得赶紧走了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And now I must run.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.30,0:26:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我来这趟耽误晚餐了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm making dinner late by being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.52,0:26:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等我们回来再见了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll see you when we get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.10,0:26:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她说得对  会很别扭的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's right. It will be strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.31,0:26:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我会怀念有个斗嘴的伴儿让我保持状态\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I shall miss having a sparring partner to keep me trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.49,0:26:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}拿那些衣服可小心点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Be careful how you handle them clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.49,0:26:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那都是高定\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They're haute couture.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我得去给玛丽小姐和赫克瑟姆夫人更衣了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I should go to Lady Mary and Lady Hexham to help them dress,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.41,0:26:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就让黛西帮您收拾行李了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so I'll leave Daisy with the unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.66,0:26:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等您去吃饭了我再来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll be back when you're at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.50,0:26:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只要我上来时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So long as it's finished
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.58,0:26:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}都收拾好了  行李箱也都收起来了就行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and the trunks are gone when I come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.50,0:26:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们怎么会在内格莱斯科酒店的屋顶上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What were you doing on the roof of the Negresco?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.96,0:26:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们在玩寻宝  需要一个烟囱顶帽\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, it was a scavenger hunt, and we needed a chimney pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.67,0:26:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可我们上去才发现  那玩意好大\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But when we got up there, they were huge,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.59,0:26:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们就砸了一个  各拿了一块\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so we smashed one and all took a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.85,0:26:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}经理怎么看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, was the manager pleased?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.31,0:26:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这有利于宣传\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it was good publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.89,0:26:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有有利宣传这种事吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is there such a thing as good publicity?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.69,0:26:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}对于拍电影来说有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There is if you're in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.15,0:27:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}俄国人会砸玻璃祈福\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I suppose the Russians smash their glasses for good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.23,0:27:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}演艺人士会砸别人的财产好获得有利宣传\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And now film people smash other people's property for good publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.03,0:27:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是这样吗  达格利什小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is this true, Miss Dalgleish?
