Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.16,0:36:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴格肖夫人和布兰森先生先生和太太\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lady Bagshaw and Mr. And Mrs. Branson.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}布兰森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ah, Monsieur Branson,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.08,0:36:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那位幸运孩子的父亲\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}father of the lucky child.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.74,0:36:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你肯定很高兴吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How happy you must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.83,0:36:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我和我妻子很高兴能来这里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My wife and I are very glad to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.54,0:36:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我得说  很感谢您愿意招待我们这一群人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I must say straightaway how kind you are to include us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.54,0:36:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们很荣幸  赫克瑟姆侯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're delighted, Lord Hexham.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.13,0:36:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吧  妈妈\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Aren't we, maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.76,0:36:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很荣幸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.51,0:36:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢  帕特莫太太\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you, Mrs. Patmore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-谢谢  -慢点吃\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Thank you. - Uh, mind you eat them slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.26,0:36:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}梅森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.89,0:36:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你好吗  你要回农场去吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How are you? Are you on your way back to the farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.19,0:36:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想让那小两口歇歇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I wanted to give the young couple a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们都没有独处时间\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They're never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.31,0:36:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}总得忍受我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They always have to put up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.77,0:36:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那是你家  你想怎样就怎样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it's your house to do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.07,0:36:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我希望他们觉得那是他们的家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I want them to feel it's their home,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这样等我不再租了  他们就会接手\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so that when I surrender the tenancy, they'll take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.36,0:36:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你打算干什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.66,0:36:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你就别担心我了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.03,0:36:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你还要操心自己的事呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You've got your own concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.83,0:36:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就是担心你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I do worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.16,0:36:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.79,0:37:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}明天的拍摄日程表一小时后发下去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Call sheets for tomorrow will be issued in an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.13,0:37:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}送到你们的房间\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and delivered to your digs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.00,0:37:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}今天还顺利吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A good day?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.17,0:37:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只要能按进度进行就算顺利\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's always good if we get through the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.46,0:37:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那是什么  好消息吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What's that? Good news, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.05,0:37:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}并不是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.76,0:37:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我丈夫要比预期的迟些回来了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My husband isn't coming back when he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.26,0:37:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}肯定很失望吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Must be a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.97,0:37:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}失望  但不意外\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a disappointment but not a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.22,0:37:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}八点半太晚了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Half past 8:00 is too late for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.77,0:37:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要七点吃饭\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I like to eat at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.27,0:37:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}改变常规时间安排很难为厨房\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's difficult for the kitchen if we change the usual timings.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.57,0:37:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我真看不出她有什么明星魔力\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I wish I could see the star magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.49,0:37:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这样吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}瑟斯克在放映她的一部电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}One of her films is showing in Thirsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.16,0:37:33.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们一起去看吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why don't we catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.45,0:37:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还是算了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I should say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.78,0:37:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}为什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.66,0:37:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的家人都不在  你可以自己做主\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}None of your family's here. You're your own mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.41,0:37:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.91,0:37:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我去告诉巴罗  换件大衣  然后告诉奶奶\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll warn Barrow, put on a coat and tell Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.05,0:37:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}奶奶  别生气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, Granny, don't be cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.72,0:37:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我要去瑟斯克看电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I'm going into Thirsk to see a film.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你自己去吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}On your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.43,0:37:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟导演巴伯先生去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}With Mr. Barber, the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.76,0:38:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亨利最近来信儿了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Have you heard from Henry lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.85,0:38:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他今天发来封电报\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He sent a telegram today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.31,0:38:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他暂时还不回来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's not coming back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.77,0:38:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}丹可  计划有变\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Denker, change of plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.94,0:38:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不更衣了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I won't get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.02,0:38:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我拿托盘吃晚餐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll have my dinner on a tray.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.57,0:38:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是  夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.37,0:38:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}抱歉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.29,0:38:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}达格利什小姐像疣一样讨厌又不怪你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's not your fault that Miss Dalgleish has all the charm of a verruca.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.12,0:38:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}德克斯特先生还挺好的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, Mr. Dexter's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.75,0:38:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他可以自己应付她  不需要我帮忙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He can stick up for himself without my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.63,0:38:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您对拍电影不感兴趣吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Doesn't filming interest you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.01,0:38:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看了看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I watched some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.30,0:38:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我宁可去吃石头\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd rather eat pebbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.93,0:38:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还是上床吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In fact, I think I'll retire to my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.01,0:38:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}至少待到他们走了为止\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}At least until they've all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.43,0:38:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我需要担心吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Should I be worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.60,0:38:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}弗洛伦斯·南丁格尔38岁就上床了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, Florence Nightingale took to her bed at the age of 38.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.77,0:38:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她90岁才死呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She died at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.52,0:38:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您会告诉我吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You would tell me, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你觉得呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.07,0:38:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你呢  格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And you, Lord Grantham?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.95,0:39:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你熟悉南法吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you familiar with the south of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.04,0:39:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道1830年代布鲁厄姆男爵做大法官时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know Lord Brougham first made it fashionable
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.25,0:39:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}最先让来南法成为了潮流\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}in the 1830s when he was chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所以你只是在拿回本就属于你的东西吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So you're only taking back what is yours by right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.51,0:39:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不会这么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I wouldn't say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.63,0:39:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我理解这为什么让你不高兴\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I do see why you find it upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.22,0:39:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你还是来了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But here you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.76,0:39:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}打量家具  丈量窗帘\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}eyeing up the furniture, measuring the curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈  拜托\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maman, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.51,0:39:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们还可以买别的别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We can always buy another villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.43,0:39:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们来是应你儿子的邀请\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're here because your son invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.35,0:39:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我想我也是想知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I suppose I would like to know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.90,0:39:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你丈夫为什么这么做\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}why your husband did what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.86,0:39:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我已经叫律师过几天来一趟了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've asked our lawyer to join us here in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.15,0:39:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得这样甚好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think it's an excellent idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.07,0:39:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在此之前  希望你们都住得愉快\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Until then, I hope you'll enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.24,0:39:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您的管家让我们的日常更加气派了  这可真棒\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Your butler lends a welcome air of splendor to the proceedings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.25,0:39:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你想  可以让他退下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But he can stand down if you prefer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.54,0:39:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}何必呢  别墅已经是你外孙女的了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why, when the villa already belongs to your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.83,0:39:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴格肖夫人  快来坐吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lady Bagshaw, please come and sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.01,0:39:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真抱歉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.67,0:39:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就闭眼躺了五分钟  就睡过去了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I laid down for five minutes, shut my eyes, and that was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.97,0:40:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}睡得沉沉的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.59,0:40:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}欢迎来到鸽子别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Welcome to the Villa of the Doves.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.22,0:40:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你们经常来吧  -是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- You must come here a lot. - We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.85,0:40:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}之前是的  在你们出现之前\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Or rather, we did, before you entered our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.85,0:40:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}自我有记忆以来  每年冬天都来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Always in the winter for as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.52,0:40:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但现在  夏季来玩也时髦了起来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But now coming in the warmer months is catching on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.27,0:40:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我打算就此写篇文章呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm planning an article on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.07,0:40:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您是作家吗  赫克瑟姆夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're a writer, Lady Hexham?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.44,0:40:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说是记者还差不多\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}More of a journalist, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.36,0:40:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我有本杂志  我打算重新掌控它\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I have a magazine, and I'm taking back control of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.32,0:40:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的文章是写什么的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What's your article about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.70,0:40:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}斯考特·菲茨杰拉德  塞尔达  可可·香奈儿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, uh, Scott Fitzgerald, Zelda, Coco Chanel.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.91,0:40:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所有让酒店七月继续迎客的人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}All the people that got the hotels to stay open in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.58,0:40:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可以发布一些别墅的照片吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Can I publish some pictures of the villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.21,0:40:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这可以吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Might that be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.92,0:40:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.13,0:40:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你发布前要让我们看看照片\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If we can see the images before you use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.22,0:40:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他显然不是第一次跟记者打交道了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ah, you're obviously not the first journalist he's met.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.26,0:40:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}请出示影票\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Tickets, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.81,0:40:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们只能改日再欣赏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're going to have to defer our appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.64,0:40:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}达格利什小姐的魅力了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}of Miss Dalgleish's attractions to another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.40,0:40:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这不是她的电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This isn't her film.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.52,0:40:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}《惊恐》是英国上映的第一部有声片\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The Terror is the first all-talking picture to show in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.19,0:41:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-不是《爵士歌手》吗  -不是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- I thought that was The Jazz Singer. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.15,0:41:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在那部里  阿尔·乔生只是对他的老母亲说了几句话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In that, Al Jolson just says a few words to his old mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.74,0:41:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还唱歌\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, and sings.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.57,0:41:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这部电影可以是从头说到尾\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In this, they talk all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.08,0:41:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}丽都影院在哪\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Where's the Rialto?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.33,0:41:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}前面左转停车\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Uh, take the next left and park.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.38,0:41:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}玛丽小姐跟巴伯先生去瑟斯克看电影了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lady Mary's gone to the pictures in Thirsk with Mr. Barber,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.01,0:41:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}格兰瑟姆老夫人要在房间里吃饭\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and old Lady Grantham's eating in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.47,0:41:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}德克斯特先生和达格利什小姐会单独进餐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So Mr. Dexter and Miss Dalgleish will be dining alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.89,0:41:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您告诉帕特莫太太了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Have you let Mrs. Patmore know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.64,0:41:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.47,0:41:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们都可怜德克斯特先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We all pity Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.14,0:41:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.60,0:41:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您不会想知道的  休斯太太\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, you wouldn't be interested, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.52,0:41:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说来听听\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Try me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你想说的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.29,0:41:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}王室来访时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When we had the royal visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.91,0:41:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您记得有个叫埃利斯的贴身男仆吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}do you remember a valet called Ellis?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.79,0:41:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}记得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.92,0:41:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我记得你和他还挺亲近的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You and he were quite friendly, I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.01,0:42:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我今早收到了一封他的来信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I had a letter from him this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.26,0:42:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说他要结婚了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}saying he's getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.60,0:42:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这让你难过吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And that's sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.39,0:42:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道我不该这么想\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know it shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.10,0:42:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴罗先生  你的人生路很艰难\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Barrow, your path in life is a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.57,0:42:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大部分与你处境相同的人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Most people in your position
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}会选择藏在假象之下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}choose to hide behind appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.36,0:42:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}以此避免遭到迫害和拒绝\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that will allow them to avoid persecution and rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.62,0:42:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他不该因此被责怪\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's surely not to be blamed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.08,0:42:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我并不想如此  休斯太太\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It isn't what I want, Mrs. Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.04,0:42:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那你是个勇敢的人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then you're a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.33,0:42:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你也注定要孤独了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But you're also destined to be a lonely one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.55,0:42:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}除非你非常幸运\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Unless you're very fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.36,0:43:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不是说她的脸能卖上百万张票吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I thought you said her face could sell a million tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.24,0:43:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看来在瑟斯克不行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not in Thirsk, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.83,0:43:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你说得没错\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But you're right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.62,0:43:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她真是漂亮\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She is very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.89,0:43:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这太棒了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How wonderful this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.81,0:43:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还是不懂为什么让我们过来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm still curious as to why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.10,0:43:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你去英国  就能见到我妈妈了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you'd come to England, you could have met Mama,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.31,0:43:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那样更合理\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}which would've made more sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.02,0:43:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我更想见你  而不是格兰瑟姆老夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It was you I wanted to meet more than old Lady Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.90,0:43:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那你母亲呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.57,0:43:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她的处境要更微妙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The situation is more delicate for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.66,0:43:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但她不会有事的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but she'll be all right.
