Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.63,0:45:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你刚到好莱坞时在卖男装\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you were selling menswear when you first got to Hollywood,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.05,0:45:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是怎么进入电影行业的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}how did you break into films?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有天  他们要求我穿一套他们在销售的西装\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, one day, they asked me to pose for a trade journal
