Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.18,0:45:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为你太帅了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Because you're so handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.56,0:45:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还以为他们是看上了我的演技呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I thought they were excited by my acting talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.77,0:45:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}姑娘们  快去换衣服吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Come on, girls. Get to wardrobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.31,0:45:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们都想回家了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We all want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.81,0:45:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在你知道我是怎么拍起电影的了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now you know why I'm in the movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.11,0:45:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是怎么当上管家的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How did you become a butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.90,0:45:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可没那么风光\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it's a lot less glamorous.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.11,0:45:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我起初是门童\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I got a job as a hallboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.65,0:45:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}然后是初级男仆  第一男仆  贴身男仆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then I was a junior footman, first footman, valet
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.57,0:45:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}最终当上了管家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and finally butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.37,0:45:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说起打理宅子  我可是无所不晓  先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There's not much I couldn't tell you about how to run a house, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.99,0:46:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这就是你和我的区别\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}See, that's the difference between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.08,0:46:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我半数时候都不知道自己在做什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't know what I'm doing half the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.21,0:46:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看上去可不像\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's not what it looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.29,0:46:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢  你是...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, thank you, Mr....?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.25,0:46:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴罗就行  先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just Barrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.88,0:46:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好了  盖  我们彩排一下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Right, Guy. Let's rehearse please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.47,0:46:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫娜  说台词\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Myrna, say the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.81,0:46:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我给你留了根木槌\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I saved you a mallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.85,0:46:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我一直觉得它们看上去像是打仗用的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I always think they look like instruments of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.23,0:46:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为本来就是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's because they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.48,0:46:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有电话找你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There's a telephone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.02,0:46:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}布洛克先生  说是急事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A Mr. Bullock. He says it's urgent.
