Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.57,0:46:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我上楼时  那个负责人在冲着电话大喊大叫\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The man in charge was shouting down the telephone when I came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.70,0:46:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看来他们拍的电影不对\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Apparently, they're making the wrong sort of film.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.20,0:46:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有对的电影吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is there a right sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.91,0:46:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我只知道  公众似乎只想看有声电影\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, all I know is it seems the public only want films that talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.50,0:46:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我以为电影最棒的地方\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I should've thought the best thing about films
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.55,0:46:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就是听不到呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}is that you can't hear them.
