Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.01,0:46:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大家都过来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Everybody, gather around, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.68,0:46:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}都过来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.39,0:47:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们要暂停拍摄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We are suspending production.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.93,0:47:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I-I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.23,0:47:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真抱歉带来坏消息\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm sorry to be the bearer of bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.56,0:47:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}计划定好后  便会联络大家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'll contact you all when we've finalized our plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.52,0:47:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.53,0:47:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么了  发生什么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What is it? What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看来有声片的热度已经不容忽视\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it seems the talkies are making too much money to ignore,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.87,0:47:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而我们拍的是默片  难以回本\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}while our picture is silent and too expensive to make its costs back,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.12,0:47:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所以他们想及时止损  中止拍摄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so they want to cut their losses and shut us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.91,0:47:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-太糟了  -对于剧组的人来说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- But how sad. - It is worse than sad
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.04,0:47:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还要更严重\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}for the men and women working on it.
