Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.49,0:48:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}为什么不能把这部电影改成有声片\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, why couldn't this be turned into a talking film?
