Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.91,0:48:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他可以给我们已经拍的戏录音\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He could record sound for scenes we've already made and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}然后给剩下的戏写新台词\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And then put new speeches into the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.88,0:48:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这难道不行吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why wouldn't that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.01,0:48:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}梅森先生要把我逼疯了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Mason's driving me mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.51,0:48:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}每个杯子碟子都要摆对地方\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Every cup and saucer has to be right.
