Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.10,0:48:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他儿子因战争而死\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}His son died in the war.
