Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.56,0:48:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可惜他这么惹你烦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it's a shame he's getting on your nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.52,0:48:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为他是个好人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}because he's a lovely chap.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.36,0:48:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他对你更是珍视  黛西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And he thinks the world of you, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.98,0:48:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你以前不还喜欢过他吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Weren't you sweet on him once?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.90,0:48:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那都多少年前的事了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}About a hundred years ago.
