Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.87,0:48:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别提醒我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.45,0:48:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您还好吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you all right?
