Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.55,0:48:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}哎呀\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.72,0:49:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这不是巴罗就行吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If it isn't Just Barrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.47,0:49:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.26,0:49:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就是在想  这栋大宅子可比\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've just been thinking how much more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.68,0:49:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们傻乎乎的电影有趣多了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}this great house is than our silly little film.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.02,0:49:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别喊我"先生"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't call me "Sir."
