Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.40,0:49:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不明白\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.07,0:49:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}电影之前一直是哑剧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Films have been mime until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.70,0:49:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}哑剧加音乐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mime with music.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.49,0:49:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在的有声片要看演技了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now with the new talkies, they're gonna be about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.16,0:49:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们不会想要我们的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They won't want us.
