Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.13,0:49:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你的声音很不错\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But you've got a good voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.17,0:49:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许会有新面孔\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There may be new faces coming in,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.80,0:49:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但公众也不会忘了所有他们最喜欢的老面孔\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but the public won't want to say goodbye to all their old favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.76,0:49:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}希望你是对的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.30,0:49:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.78,0:49:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那是公爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's the Duke...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.44,0:50:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}威斯敏斯特公爵的游艇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's the Duke of Westminster's yacht.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.85,0:50:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是这样的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Let me sum up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.64,0:50:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}自1864年以来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In the years since 1864,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.77,0:50:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}过世的蒙米拉侯爵立过四份遗嘱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}the late Marquis de Montmirail made four wills.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.65,0:50:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他在每一封里都提到\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In every one, he refers to the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.86,0:50:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他1865年就将鸽子别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that he gave the Villa des Colombes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.28,0:50:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}送给了如今的格兰瑟姆老伯爵夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to the now Dowager Countess of Grantham in 1865.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.16,0:50:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我带来了原件\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I brought the originals.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.62,0:50:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}复件我留给你们\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I will leave copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.16,0:50:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那他显然不是忘了这回事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then clearly it wasn't something that slipped his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.70,0:50:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他的确想这么做  而且一直没改主意\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He meant to do this thing, and he stuck by his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.04,0:50:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这让我好受些了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I feel better for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.25,0:50:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她肯定抓住了他什么把柄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She must have had some hold over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.17,0:50:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她肯定是勒索了他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She must have blackmailed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.71,0:50:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈  这么想太傻了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maman, this is a foolish response.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.75,0:51:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们会告上法庭的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We shall challenge it in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.80,0:51:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有什么理由呢  夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}On what basis, madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.97,0:51:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您还有其他房子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You have other houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.34,0:51:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}困苦不是理由\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There's no question of hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.14,0:51:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您丈夫买下别墅并做处理时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Your husband bought the villa and disposed of it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.43,0:51:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还不认识您呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}before he even met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.43,0:51:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我建议您尽快把别墅交出来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My advice would be to surrender the property without delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.61,0:51:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}非常感谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.11,0:51:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你打算接受吗  -当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Do you mean to accept this? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.03,0:51:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我父亲指名我为唯一的遗嘱执行人  格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My father made me sole executor, Lord Grantham.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.16,0:51:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得这是因为他相信我会执行他的遗愿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I like to think it was because he trusted me to carry out his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.62,0:51:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那你为什么邀请我们来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then why did you invite us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.25,0:51:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为我很想见你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Because I was curious to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.96,0:51:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我父亲和你母亲在1864年10月共度了一周\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My father and your mother spent a week together in October 1864.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.51,0:51:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我是1865年7月出生的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I was born in July 1865.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.63,0:51:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没错\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.05,0:51:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想他正是因此才在一个月后就把别墅送给了她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think that's the key to why he gave her the villa one month later.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.60,0:51:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是为了庆祝你的出生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In gratitude for your birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.52,0:51:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就是说  我相信我们有很多共同点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In short, I believe you and I have a great deal in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.66,0:52:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我们应该感谢老夫人  -当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- We should thank old Lady Grantham. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.21,0:52:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}至少我们现在知道  她得到别墅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}At least now we know that for her to have the villa
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.42,0:52:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}并非是因一时兴起或愚蠢失误\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}wasn't a random choice or a foolish mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.25,0:52:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而是一个多年来未变的决定\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but a decision that was firmly endorsed over many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.09,0:52:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这感觉怪怪的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Feels funny, in a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.84,0:52:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我的孩子属于这样一个黄金圈子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to know my own child is part of this golden circle
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.05,0:52:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只因为血统就能遇上好事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}where, because of your blood, lovely things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.43,0:52:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就像玛丽会得到唐顿  我们会得到布朗普顿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just as Mary will have Downton and we will have Brompton.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.52,0:52:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是  但那都是运营庄园\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes, but they're working estates.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.23,0:52:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这地方就是玩乐用的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This place was made for laughter and fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.85,0:52:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}茜玻难道不会为自己的女儿感到开心吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Wouldn't Sybil have been pleased for her daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.98,0:52:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}并鼓励她用它来帮助他人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And encouraged her to use it for the good of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.86,0:52:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊  她会的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes, I think she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.24,0:52:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那我们也这么做吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then let's do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.62,0:52:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我真想带茜玻来这里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I long to bring Sybbie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.99,0:52:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她肯定会喜欢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She'll love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.58,0:52:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看这景色多美\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Look at that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.91,0:53:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}难道不让你对生活充满感激吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't you feel grateful we're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.13,0:53:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我爱你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I love you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.38,0:53:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我都没想到自己还能再这样爱一个人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In a way I thought I'd never love again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.38,0:53:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也爱你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.51,0:53:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所以这正好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.06,0:53:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们回去吧  这水...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Shall we go back in? The water is...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.93,0:53:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们看上去好幸福\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They look very happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.14,0:53:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这就对了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So they should.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.10,0:53:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这对茜玻  对他们都是天大的好事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's thrilling for Sybbie, for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.40,0:53:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我希望汤姆和露西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I like the idea of Tom and Lucy
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.98,0:53:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}每年夏季都能在这里举办聚会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}hosting a gathering here every summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.53,0:53:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}直到这成为家族传统\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}until it becomes a family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.16,0:53:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}太阳晒得我昏昏欲睡\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The sun has made me sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.24,0:53:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}失陪  我想在晚饭前打个盹\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you'll excuse me, I think I'll have a nap before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.79,0:53:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你看上去也有点累\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You look a little tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.75,0:53:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你也去睡吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why don't you do the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.58,0:53:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我待会儿就去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I won't be too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.30,0:53:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她说得对  您是看上去很累\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's right. You do look tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.13,0:53:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说出来也没什么用吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Never sure how helpful it is for people to point it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.55,0:53:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}抱歉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.56,0:53:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不管怎样  你要一直写作\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Keep writing, whatever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.35,0:54:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈  如果您有烦恼  请说出来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mama, if something is troubling you, please just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.06,0:54:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不  没事  真的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No, no, it's nothing, honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.23,0:54:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我又不得不更改了晚餐桌的摆放\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've had to change the setting of the dinner table again,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.11,0:54:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他们好像总算学会怎么给老爷熨衣服了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I think they've got the hang of ironing His Lordship's shirts at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.49,0:54:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您该让我去的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You should've let me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.87,0:54:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们肯定很感激您的帮助  卡森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They must be very grateful for your help, Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.37,0:54:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.20,0:54:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我教他们做的时候\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When I showed them how to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.25,0:54:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们很快很大声地用法语说了一堆话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}they certainly spoke a lot of French very loud and very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.63,0:54:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}事情定下了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is anything settled yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.25,0:54:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别墅现在是茜玻小姐的了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It seems the villa now belongs to Miss Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.26,0:54:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真幸运\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lucky girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.51,0:54:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你羡慕她吗  巴克斯特小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Do you envy her, Miss Baxter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.97,0:54:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不相信羡慕  贝茨先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not a big believer in envy, Mr. Bates.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.47,0:54:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道我想要什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.68,0:54:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有南法的别墅对我来说也无所谓\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I can live without a villa in the south of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.98,0:54:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你想要什么  巴克斯特小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What do you want, Miss Baxter?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.10,0:54:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}得了  卡森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, come now, Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.73,0:54:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们都知道巴克斯特小姐想要什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We all know what Miss Baxter wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.27,0:54:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她的爱恋可是坚定不移\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Her affections are very firmly engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.73,0:54:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还没"订"呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.82,0:54:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许是还没订婚  但完全沉迷其中了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not engaged in that way, perhaps, but thoroughly taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.82,0:54:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们是在说莫斯利先生吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are we discussing Mr. Molesley?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.08,0:54:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.87,0:55:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但如果他一直没提出来呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But suppose he never steps up to the mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.66,0:55:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那我就做个老处女\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then I will be a spinster.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.87,0:55:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不会嫁给别人吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You'd never marry anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.29,0:55:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我找到他都花了那么久\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It took me long enough to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.42,0:55:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.05,0:55:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不知道他考虑多久了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't know how long he's thought about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.85,0:55:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他查了日期后就确信了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but once he checked the dates, he was sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.02,0:55:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我的生日正是在他们那段\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was born exactly nine months after-- and I quote--
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.15,0:55:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"诗意的短暂情缘"九个月后\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}the "idyllic interlude" they spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.52,0:55:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他在我出生后不久就把别墅送给了她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And he gave her the villa soon after I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.82,0:55:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这肯定都是巧合\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm sure that's all coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.74,0:55:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.36,0:55:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这就能解释这个谜团了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It would explain the mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.90,0:55:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你父亲非常爱你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Your father loved you very much.
