Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.00,1:03:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-对帕特莫太太怎么想  -不行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- About Mrs. Patmore. - You can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.21,1:03:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么不行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.96,1:03:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你知道她有自己的房子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You know she's got a house of her own.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.80,1:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而且她很孤单\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You know she's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.30,1:03:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这对我们都是条好出路\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a solution for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.97,1:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们像是在谋划什么呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You look very conspiratorial.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.18,1:03:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们在谈论帕特莫太太呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We were talking about Mrs. Patmore
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.68,1:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有她是多喜欢你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and how much she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.31,1:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Does she indeed?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.10,1:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也喜欢她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I like her.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.56,1:03:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-她是个好女人  -是啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- She's a fine woman. - She is.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.60,1:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我有时担心她太孤单了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I worry sometimes that she's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.90,1:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她有自己的农舍\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's got her own cottage, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.36,1:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我觉得她会想要个伴儿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I think she'd like some company in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.70,1:03:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道你在想什么  但不行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know what you're thinking, but the answer's no.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.07,1:04:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不是一直说你欣赏她吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You've always said you admired her.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.99,1:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}的确\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And so I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.16,1:04:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我不能让个女人养活\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I couldn't live off a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.45,1:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那怎么行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It wouldn't be right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.75,1:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-哪怕她愿意吗  -是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Even if she wanted it? - Even then.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.58,1:04:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有些事是对的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There are things that are right
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.79,1:04:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有些事是错的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and there are things that are wrong,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.33,1:04:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这我无力改变\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I can't change that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.67,1:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢你帮忙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you for taking it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.43,1:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我欠你个大人情\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I owe you a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.76,1:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一切都还好吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is everything in order?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.89,1:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等我们给已经拍好的戏录好音\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, once we've recorded sound for the scenes we've already shot,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.26,1:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就得给剩下的内容写新本子了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}we'll need new material for what's left...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.31,1:04:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可以说两句吗  巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}M-May I have a word, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.56,1:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}请吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.61,1:04:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看了所有如果电影是默片\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I-I've been through all the dialogue cards
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.57,1:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}会放映出来的对话卡\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that w-would've been shown if the picture were silent,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.15,1:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}于是便开始编写\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I've started to sketch out scenes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.49,1:04:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}能满足剧情需要的戏份\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that would cover the needs of the plot.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.41,1:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是说你写了剧本吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You mean you've written a play?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.87,1:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}至少开始写了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I've started one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.99,1:04:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-可以给我看看吗  -当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Could I read these scenes? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.83,1:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你满意  我再继续写\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And if you're content, I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.67,1:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我必须按剧情梗概走吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Am I bound by the plot synopsis?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.09,1:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}比如  她最终甩了他时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}For instance, when she finally casts him off,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.17,1:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是不是安排一场浪漫的高潮戏更好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}might it not be better with a big romantic climax?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.93,1:05:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不明白\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.22,1:05:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}比尔·本森就要把身家都丢在赌桌上了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, Bill Benson's about to throw away his life on the tables.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.47,1:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他空虚  孤独  毫无希望\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Alone, hollow and without hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.15,1:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}突然  他抬起头\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then suddenly he lifts his face
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.27,1:05:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看到安就站在那里  高挑  平静  优雅\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and sees Anne standing there, tall, serene, graceful,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.32,1:05:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她眼里饱含泪水  闪闪发亮\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}her eyes shining with unshed tears.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.03,1:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他一个冲动  把钱都揽了回来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}On an impulse, he snatches back his money.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.20,1:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}停止下注\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Rien ne va plus!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.37,1:05:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}轮盘旋转\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The wheel spins.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.63,1:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他原本会输掉一切\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And every last thing he owns would have gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.13,1:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But no.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.93,1:05:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她的爱和美拯救了他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Her love, her beauty have saved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.43,1:05:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她握起他的手  他们离开了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She takes his hand, and they walk away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.77,1:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一起退场\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Together.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.31,1:05:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}完\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The end.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.82,1:05:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要哭了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.48,1:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫斯利先生  请按你的心意\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Molesley, please finish the script
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.36,1:06:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}完成剧本  然后拿给我看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}however you think best and bring it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.57,1:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.24,1:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你说他以前在这里工作吗  -对\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- You say he used to work here? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.37,1:06:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他是个男仆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He was a footman.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.25,1:06:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我们并不知他还有隐藏的才华\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But we weren't aware of his hidden talents.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.55,1:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可怜的卡森  他这身厚衣服肯定热死了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Poor Carson. He must be cooking in those heavy clothes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.51,1:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有轻便点的衣服可以给他吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Isn't there a lighter version he could wear?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.01,1:06:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-应该有  -谢谢  先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- I believe so. - Thank you, monsieur,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.10,1:06:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我们英国人是不会嫌穿对的衣服太热的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but we English are never too hot to wear the correct attire.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.60,1:06:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我明天请了些朋友来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've invited some friends tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.98,1:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟你们道别  并介绍你们\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to say goodbye and introduce all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.10,1:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你的管家让我意识到\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But the presence of your butler reminds me
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.86,1:06:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们现在是你们的客人了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that we are now your guests
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.81,1:06:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}应该请求你们的准许\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I should have asked your permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.40,1:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别客气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.82,1:06:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}让我们为你幸运的外孙女茜玻·布兰森举杯吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Let us drink to your fortunate granddaughter, Sybil Branson.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.61,1:06:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-敬茜玻  -茜玻\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- To Sybbie. - Sybbie.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.70,1:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她要是在就好了  我真想见见她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I wish she were here. I should like to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.83,1:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}希望你有天能见到她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I hope you will one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.95,1:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她很可爱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's a lovely girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.08,1:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很高兴听到一位继母这么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's nice to hear a stepmother talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.83,1:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你对事情的发展很满意吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You must be pleased the way things have turned out.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.04,1:06:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当你爱的人被幸运眷顾\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When people you love have a stroke of luck,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.58,1:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}简直比自己走运还美妙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}it's almost better than being lucky yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.25,1:06:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊  但也不一样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Almost but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.84,1:07:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.55,1:07:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}书房里的那些小画像\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You know the miniatures in the library?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.89,1:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}其中有一副是奶奶的  侧面还刻了字\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}One of them is of Granny, and it's engraved on the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.94,1:07:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看到过\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've seen it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.40,1:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我半个多世纪以来都不得不看到它\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I have been obliged to see it there for more than half a century.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.11,1:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他不许我动它\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But he forbade me to move it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.66,1:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他还逼我起誓\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He made me swear.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.83,1:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有塔伯特先生的新消息吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Any more news from Mr. Talbot?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.96,1:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}自我给你看过的电报后就没有了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not since the cable I showed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.12,1:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您很想他吧  小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You must be missing him, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.96,1:07:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}希望他也想我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I just hope he misses me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.34,1:07:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}老爷很快就会回家了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}His Lordship will be home soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.22,1:07:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他恐怕要震惊了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm afraid he'll be in for a shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.01,1:07:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你喜欢看电影拍摄吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Have you enjoyed the filming?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.14,1:07:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还算喜欢吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.14,1:07:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我喜欢巴伯先生和德克斯特先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I like Mr. Barber and Mr. Dexter
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.47,1:07:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}也喜欢看电影的拍摄\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and watching how a film is made, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.81,1:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但也有点失望\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I feel a bit let down, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.11,1:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为达格利什小姐吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}By Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.56,1:08:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}听上去很蠢  但\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It sounds stupid, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.78,1:08:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还以为我们能成为朋友呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I thought we might become friends.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.32,1:08:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}据说见到你最喜欢的明星可能是个错误\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They say it can be a mistake to meet your favorite stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.99,1:08:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这次算是说对了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In this case, they'd be right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.37,1:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}*疯狂韵律  门在那里*\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}*Crazy rhythm, here's the doorway*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.87,1:08:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}*我走我的  你走你的*\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}*I go my way, you go your way...*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.75,1:08:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我也是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So do I.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.05,1:08:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你开心吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you feeling happy?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.55,1:08:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的  但还得辛苦一番呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I am, but there's work to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.47,1:08:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}越是辛苦  你就越开心\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And the more hard work involved, the happier you'll be.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.18,1:08:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你真了解我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, you know me already.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.01,1:08:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的  我想享受茜玻的好运\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And, yes, I mean to enjoy Sybbie's good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.47,1:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我希望我们都能享受其中\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I want us all to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.56,1:08:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恭喜  汤姆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Congratulations, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.10,1:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你算是成功地改变了自己\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're a leopard who has successfully changed his spots.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.94,1:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}*疯狂韵律  我也发了疯*\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}*Crazy rhythm, I've gone crazy, too...*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.11,1:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}*疯狂韵律  我也发了疯*\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}*Crazy rhythm, I've gone crazy, too.*
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.74,1:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}它太快了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ah, he's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.58,1:08:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-再来  -不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Another one. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.41,1:08:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}球呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Where's the ball?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.12,1:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}它跑了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.92,1:09:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}打得好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Ah, good hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.79,1:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.09,1:09:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}乔治该去上床了  至少该准备了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}George should be in bed, or at least on his way there.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.76,1:09:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你还有别的孩子吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Do you have other children?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.72,1:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟第二任丈夫生的女儿  卡罗琳\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A daughter, Caroline, with my second husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.35,1:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}乔治的父亲七年前死于了一场车祸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}George's father was killed in a car accident seven years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.72,1:09:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就在乔治出生那天\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}on the day George was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.14,1:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他抱过了宝宝  然后死在了回家的路上\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He held the baby in his arms and died on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.35,1:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}天啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}My God.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.11,1:09:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他什么样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.03,1:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他很完美\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He was perfect, really.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.07,1:09:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}像童话里的王子一样帅气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}As handsome as a prince in a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.91,1:09:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}正直  坚强  很有梦想  也有责任心\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Moral, strong, full of dreams, determined to do his bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.58,1:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你想他吗  -当然\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Do you miss him? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.08,1:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我有时会想\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Although I sometimes wonder
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.08,1:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果他还活着  会变成什么样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}what life would've made of him if he'd lived.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.09,1:09:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在有些地方...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In a way...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.17,1:09:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In a way?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.72,1:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我是想说  你有点让我想起了他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was going to say, in a way, you remind me of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.55,1:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我说不上来为什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Although I couldn't tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.10,1:09:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我很荣幸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.64,1:09:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你现任丈夫呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What about your present husband?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.47,1:09:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亨利要务实得多\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, Henry's much more pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.56,1:10:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他不做梦  而是实干\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There are no dreams about him. He's a doer.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.44,1:10:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他总是没日没夜地测试自己的忍耐力\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And he must test his powers of endurance from morning till night.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.32,1:10:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他是个好搭档\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But he's a good workmate.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.98,1:10:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他也帅吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is he handsome, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.53,1:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.74,1:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我喜欢帅的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I like them handsome.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.82,1:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但天堂也有烦恼吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But there's trouble in paradise?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.99,1:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不需要我告诉你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You don't need me to tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.25,1:10:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}婚姻是小说  不是短篇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that marriage is a novel, not a short story.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.37,1:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一路上有各种情节转折\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Full of plot twists along the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.38,1:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想最终还是要看你爱不爱他吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Suppose it comes down to whether or not you love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.46,1:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不是吧  巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Really, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.38,1:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}难道是因为你是拍电影的吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is this because you work in the films?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.68,1:10:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得我今晚说得太多了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think I've said more than enough for one evening.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.72,1:10:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}请大家热情地欢迎别墅的继承人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So I hope you will warmly welcome our successors of the villa.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.56,1:10:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟布兰森夫妇站在一起的是格兰瑟姆伯爵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And with the Bransons, perhaps you'll see Lord Grantham,
