Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.68,1:18:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们知道怎么跟她讲道理\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You know how to reason with her.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.06,1:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们不会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.07,1:18:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫娜  亲爱的  请下来吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Myrna, darling, please come down.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.57,1:18:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们没有你就拍不了戏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We can't do anything without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.57,1:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们没有我还能说话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You can talk without me!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.36,1:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}走开\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.95,1:18:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.33,1:18:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得不如让女仆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think it would be a good idea to let the maids
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.46,1:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去试试安抚她  巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}see if they can make her comfortable, Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.00,1:18:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好  那就听你的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}All right. If you think so, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.17,1:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}都退后\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Stand back, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.59,1:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}请让我们进去  达格利什小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Please let us in, Miss Dalgleish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.05,1:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们能理解你的困境\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We understand what you're going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.68,1:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你知道我们说的是真话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's true, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.89,1:19:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不会下去任由他们羞辱  嘲笑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not going down just so they can humiliate me and laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.91,1:19:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们不会的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.61,1:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你真该听到他们每次首映时都怎么说的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You should've heard them at every premiere.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.94,1:19:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"别说话  别张嘴"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}"Don't speak. Don't open your mouth."
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.73,1:19:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们鄙视我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They despise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.28,1:19:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您怎么不学学演说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why didn't you take elocution lessons?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.86,1:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很多人都在学\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lots of people do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.86,1:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我试过  但我学不会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I tried. I couldn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.45,1:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}怎么都抓不到诀窍\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Couldn't get the knack.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.82,1:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}自从你来到这里  就在为什么事生气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Something's upset you since the day you got here.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.74,1:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-是什么  -就是这事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- What is it? - It's this.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.00,1:19:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我一看到《爵士歌手》就知道自己完了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I knew I was finished the moment I saw The Jazz Singer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.04,1:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就像一把悬在我头上的剑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's been like a sword hanging over me.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.04,1:19:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还以为自己还能再拍几部戏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I thought maybe I had a few more films ahead of me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.71,1:19:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但这部就是我的最后一部了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but this one will be me last.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.13,1:19:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那可未必\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.17,1:19:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看到的那些片段里你挺不错的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You look good in the bits I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.59,1:19:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可我的声音呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And how do I sound, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.05,1:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}事实就是  像美国人说的  我过气了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But the fact is I'm washed up, as the Yanks say.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.55,1:19:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我是明日黄花了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm yesterday's news.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.81,1:19:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}得了  大小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Come on, lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.47,1:19:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这里又不是你的影迷俱乐部\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're not talking to your fan club now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.60,1:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.31,1:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你有名  美丽  还有钱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're famous, beautiful and rich.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.48,1:19:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}即便你的电影事业结束了又如何\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So what if your film career is over?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.73,1:19:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你还能做很多事呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There's any number of things you can do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.23,1:19:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}振作起来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, dust yourself off.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.82,1:19:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}顺便  对服务你的人态度好点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And while you're at it, try being polite to the people who serve you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.53,1:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}够了  黛西\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Come on, Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.03,1:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是我们的一员  不是他们的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're one of us, not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.41,1:20:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别忘了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just remember it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.58,1:20:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}快点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, chop-chop.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.58,1:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}整理一下  我们该走了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Straighten your hair, and let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.21,1:20:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你怎么样了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.58,1:20:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她快好了  巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She's almost ready, Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.88,1:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你准备好了吧  达格利什小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You are, aren't you, Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.93,1:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我以前有个妹妹跟你一样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I had a sister just like you once.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.10,1:20:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我好想她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I miss her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.43,1:20:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}每天都想\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.89,1:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你让我想到了她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You remind me of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.44,1:20:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她1919年因西班牙流感而死\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She died of the Spanish flu in 1919.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.57,1:20:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还以为我们家不会有事呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Didn't think it would touch our family,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.82,1:20:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可天不遂人愿啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but you never know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.11,1:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们走吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.67,1:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不值得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not worth it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.38,1:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你对我来说值得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're worth it to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.34,1:20:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}停止下注\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Rien ne va plus.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.27,1:21:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看来你是我的救星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It seems you're my savior.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.27,1:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我准备今后还要长长久久地做你的救星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I intend to remain your savior for a very long time to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.40,1:21:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}玛丽\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mary?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.36,1:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是怎么回事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.65,1:21:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}停\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Cut!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.57,1:21:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.99,1:21:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您让他们知道规矩了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So you put them to rights?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.53,1:21:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想我可以这么说  不会有人反驳的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think I can say so without fear of contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.00,1:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我让他们明确地知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I left them in no doubt as to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.37,1:21:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么才叫妥当\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}how things are done when they are done properly.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.96,1:21:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吧  贝茨先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Eh, Mr. Bates?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.83,1:21:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您说得非常明白\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Uh, you made your feelings clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.25,1:21:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们绝对是知道英国管家有多不好惹了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They certainly know what it is to deal with an English butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.38,1:21:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去拿衣服吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, get your coats.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.13,1:21:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看到你时  我想到了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Watching you, it took me back to the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.18,1:21:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们三个以前在阁楼上演的戏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}plays you three used to put on in the attic.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.68,1:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}只不过这次事关要更重大些\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Except there's rather more riding on it this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.85,1:21:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我无意挑刺  可我们怎么知道她能行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't mean to be harsh, but how do we know she's any good?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.56,1:21:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她好极了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, she's absolutely superb.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.77,1:21:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我把爸爸的电报给奶奶看了  汤姆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I showed Granny Papa's telegram, Tom,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.23,1:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你该去看看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but you ought to look in.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.69,1:21:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们现在就去吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Perhaps we should go up now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.15,1:22:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.65,1:22:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}该由你来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It ought to be you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.86,1:22:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你把小画像交给她吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You can give her the miniature.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.16,1:22:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么小画像\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What miniature is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.41,1:22:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说来话长\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.21,1:22:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有声片对于西区剧院的演员肯定是好事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Talkies must be good news for the actors in the West End theaters.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.67,1:22:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}对他们是好事  对我是坏事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Good news for them, bad news for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.13,1:22:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}麦克风致死  是吧  盖\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Death by microphone, eh, Guy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.42,1:22:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们这行本就是赌运气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Our business has always been a game of chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.84,1:22:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说得好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well said.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.06,1:22:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我有个主意  达格利什小姐  或许能帮你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I have an idea, Miss Dalgleish, which might just help.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.94,1:22:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我明天一早就带你妈妈去医院\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm taking your mama to the hospital first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.23,1:22:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我当然很害怕\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm dreading it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.27,1:22:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但这话能说给你听  不能说给她听\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But that's for you to hear, not her.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.69,1:22:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还以为他们会抵抗一番呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I thought they might put up more of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.24,1:22:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们也以为\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So did we.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.41,1:22:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那母亲是想抵抗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The mother wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.70,1:22:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}然后伊迪丝发现了这个\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And then Edith found this.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.12,1:22:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}侧面刻了您的名字\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's inscribed to you on the side.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.92,1:23:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.76,1:23:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们大概以为我们之间有什么越轨的事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose they think something improper went on between us.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.31,1:23:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-大家都这么想吧  -没有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- I suppose everyone does. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.35,1:23:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可不会那么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I-I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.77,1:23:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你真不会撒谎  汤姆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're such a bad liar, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.98,1:23:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要像你那么不会撒谎肯定寸步难行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd never have got anywhere if I were as rotten a liar as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.03,1:23:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们会尽量每年都在别墅相见\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're going to try and meet at the villa every year.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.78,1:23:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一家人  一起度夏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The whole family together, in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.03,1:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那不热吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Won't it be too hot?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.95,1:23:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我们希望您可以去试试看  -不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- We hope you'll come and find out. - Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.21,1:23:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.17,1:23:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我早过了那年纪了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's-that's all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.46,1:23:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}算了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.17,1:23:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我很高兴认识了你  汤姆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I am happy to have known you, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.80,1:23:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们最终相处得还不错  是吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think we got on pretty well in the end, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.93,1:23:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think we did.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.26,1:23:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}最终\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.51,1:23:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你并不是我们希望茜玻嫁的人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You weren't quite what we had in mind for Sybil,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.56,1:23:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我们都接受了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but we got past it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.39,1:23:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}生活不就是这样吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And that's life, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.02,1:23:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}接受始料未及的事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Getting past the unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.56,1:24:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许从中吸取教训\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And perhaps learning from it,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.73,1:24:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想我们做到了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}which I think we can say we've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.61,1:24:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您这些年是我的好朋友  维奥莱特\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You've been a good friend to me through the years, Violet.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.36,1:24:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}希望我也是您的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I hope I've been a friend to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.32,1:24:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在你也有家了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And now you're settled.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.53,1:24:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫德回归了家族  大家都高兴了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maud's back in the family, and everyone's happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.83,1:24:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}小画像是什么时候画的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When was the miniature painted?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.21,1:24:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您还做模特了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Did you sit for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.96,1:24:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有  我们有天\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No, we... we went for a walk
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.51,1:24:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去城里散步\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}in the town one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.47,1:24:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有家店铺里  有个男人在拍照\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and there was a shop where a man was taking photographs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.76,1:24:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我记得很清楚  因为他是我见过的第一个摄影师\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yeah, I remember 'cause he was the first photographer I'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.64,1:24:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们肯定是照那个画的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They must have copied it from that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.94,1:24:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}蒙米拉把它给我寄到了伦敦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Montmirail sent it to me in London
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.90,1:24:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还附了一封胡言乱语的信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}with a silly scribbled letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.90,1:24:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我把它寄了回去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I sent it back.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.65,1:24:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不过我该把它烧掉的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Of course, I should have burned it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.61,1:24:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们不打扰您休息了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'll leave you to rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.07,1:24:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我们想说  我们非常感激\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But we wanted to say how very grateful we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.49,1:24:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}茜玻也会感激的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And Sybbie will be, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.37,1:24:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那里很美\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's a beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.79,1:24:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这我记得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.31,1:25:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}该上床了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Time for bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.60,1:25:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}嗯  我把这些收拾一下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes, I'll just tidy these up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.44,1:25:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.82,1:25:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}蒙米拉先生的信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The letters of Monsieur de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.78,1:25:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}都标注了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They're clearly labeled?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.32,1:25:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恐怕是的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.62,1:25:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所以她说她什么都不记得了是在撒谎\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So she was lying when she said she remembers nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.99,1:25:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"撒谎"有点重了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}"Lying" is a harsh word.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.25,1:25:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}或许她是选择遗忘了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maybe she pushed it to the back of her mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.04,1:25:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在闹成这样  恐怕又回忆起来了吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I don't believe it stayed there with all the fuss going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.50,1:25:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等我去见她时再问她吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll ask when I go and see her.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.65,1:26:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴罗先生在这里吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is this the way to find Mr. Barrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.24,1:26:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}往左走\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Left.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.24,1:26:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你就藏在这里啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So this is where you hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.75,1:26:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}需要我帮什么忙吗  先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Can I help with anything, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.66,1:26:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可以帮个忙  别再喊我"先生"了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, you can certainly help by not calling me "Sir."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.25,1:26:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不知道卡森先生会怎么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not sure what Mr. Carson would make of
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.71,1:26:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我接待一位来自楼上的客人  德克斯特先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}my receiving a visit from an upstairs guest, Mr. Dexter.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.55,1:26:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}卡森先生现在又不管事了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, Mr. Carson isn't in charge now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.84,1:26:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你才是管事的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You are.
