Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.78,1:26:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}昆丁·赛博姆\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Quentin Sidebotham.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.08,1:26:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}改得好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That was a good decision.
