Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.50,1:27:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可能会联系克里夫·布洛克或查理·卓别林\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I might call Clive Brook or Charlie Chaplin,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.26,1:27:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}问他们怎么看\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}see what they think.
