Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.72,1:27:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我住在汉考克公园\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I live in a place called Hancock Park,
