Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.75,1:27:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可以照顾我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}...you could do it.
