Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.09,1:27:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不止如此\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}More than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.34,1:27:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你打理家里  安排我们的行程\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You'd run the house and organize our journeys,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.22,1:27:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}让我过得舒服\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}make me comfortable.
