Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.77,1:28:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的事业不会完的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Your career won't fold.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.77,1:28:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.81,1:28:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.57,1:28:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等你想好了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You let me know when you've...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.15,1:28:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就告诉我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}come to a decision.
