Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.63,1:28:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你觉得乐观吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But do you feel optimistic?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.63,1:28:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}罗伯特  这种话没有意义\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Robert, there's no point in that sort of talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.76,1:28:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}格兰瑟姆夫人太懂行了  我没法糊弄她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Lady Grantham knows too much to pull the wool over her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.51,1:28:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但即便真的糟得不能再糟了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But even if everything is as bad as it could be,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.64,1:28:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还可以手术吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}there's still a surgery.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.01,1:28:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们一步步来吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Let's take it one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.56,1:28:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}天啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, God.
