Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.56,1:28:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}有多少人面对这种情况时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How many have to face this kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.94,1:28:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}觉得自己虚度了人生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}feeling they've wasted their lives?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.90,1:28:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可不觉得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.28,1:28:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}完全不觉得\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not at all.
