Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.83,1:29:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}拥挤\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Cramped.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.33,1:29:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可怜的梅森先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Poor Mr. Mason.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.50,1:29:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他要是听到你这么说会很难过的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He'd be so unhappy to hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.87,1:29:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他近来总提起你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's been talking about you lately.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.17,1:29:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.50,1:29:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}说你是个好女人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Saying what a fine woman you are
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.38,1:29:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他很欣赏你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and how much he admires you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.46,1:29:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗  真的吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Does he? Really?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.47,1:29:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但他不愿更进一步了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But he won't take it any further.
