Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.84,1:29:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为他不能请你搬去农场住\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Because he can't ask you to live at the farm
