Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.77,1:29:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, couldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.52,1:29:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们走着瞧吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.36,1:29:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}看我们找到了什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Look what we've found.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.53,1:29:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我翻维奥莱特的东西时发现的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When I was going through Violet's things.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.20,1:29:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"蒙米拉侯爵的信件"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}"The letters of the Marquis de Montmirail."
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.53,1:29:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}天啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.41,1:29:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这对爸爸来说不是好事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It doesn't look good for Papa
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.45,1:29:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果她觉得有必要对此保密的话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}if she felt the need to keep it a secret.
