Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.87,1:29:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.75,1:29:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可以单独跟你说句话吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could I speak to you alone for a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.38,1:29:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.63,1:29:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在怎么办\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So what happens now?
