Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.22,1:30:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们再把消息告诉爸爸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And we'll break the news to Papa.
