Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.02,1:30:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你得帮帮我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.31,1:30:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们正准备拍最后一幕戏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're just about to film our last set piece,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.69,1:30:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}晚宴戏  本森意识到他必须放弃她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}the-the dinner when Benson realizes he must give her up
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.28,1:30:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}然后赶去了伦敦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and rushes off to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.45,1:30:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道  我刚刚还在练呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know. I've just been learning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.03,1:30:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫斯利写得真好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Molesley's done a wonderful job.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.57,1:30:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我跟你说过  群演受够了没钱拿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I told you the extras were fed up with not being paid,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.37,1:30:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不怪他们\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I don't blame them,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.83,1:30:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我还在等钱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but I'm still waiting for the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.46,1:30:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们不会做什么太过分的事吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, they won't do anything too drastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.46,1:30:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Won't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.37,1:30:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们说他们罢工了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They say they're not coming into work.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.09,1:30:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我要怎么帮忙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But how can I help?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.46,1:30:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的仆人可以替他们吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could your servants stand in?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.97,1:30:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可以去问问他们\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're welcome to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.89,1:30:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}还有别的事吗  巴伯先生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is there something else, Mr. Barber?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.56,1:30:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没有你  我根本完不成这一切\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I could never have got through any of this without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.07,1:31:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果真是这样  那我很高兴\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If that's true, then I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.62,1:31:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可以吻你吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}May I kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.33,1:31:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.04,1:31:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不想吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't you want to?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.08,1:31:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恐怕我这人太老派  我不认为\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm afraid I'm too old-fashioned to believe that
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.38,1:31:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可以只考虑自己\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}what I want is the only thing that matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.76,1:31:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-我冒犯你了吗  -完全没有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Have I offended you? - Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.97,1:31:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}对于一个已婚的老女人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nothing is nicer for an old married woman
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.39,1:31:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没什么比得知她仍令人心动更妙了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}than to find she's still an object of desire.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.35,1:31:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}等你丈夫回来  你最好别告诉他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, you better not tell your husband when he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.14,1:31:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他可能会打我的鼻子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He might, uh, hit me on the nose.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.27,1:31:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那多让人激动啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mm, wouldn't that be thrilling?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.82,1:31:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}两个帅气的男人为我争风吃醋\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Two gorgeous men fighting for my favors.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.61,1:31:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您按铃了  小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You rang, milady?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.11,1:31:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-她还留下了他的信  -看来是一封都没丢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- So she'd kept his letters? - Seemingly. Every one.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.24,1:31:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就不问她想隐瞒什么了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I won't ask what she had to hide,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.04,1:31:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}以防你们告诉我答案\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}in case you tell me the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.91,1:31:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}大部分还挺哀伤的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, most of them are rather sad.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.37,1:31:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他和他妻子显然并没什么感情\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There was clearly no love lost between him and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.58,1:31:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但信里是怎么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But what do they tell us about
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.54,1:32:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们在法国的那段日子的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}the days they spent together in France?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.30,1:32:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恐怕他们那段日子里没通信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm afraid that they didn't write to each other then.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.84,1:32:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}所以我们还是无法证明究竟发生了什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So we still have no proof of what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.09,1:32:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恐怕谜题就在这里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose that is where the mystery resides.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.05,1:32:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我明天来见维奥莱特\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll come and see Violet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.68,1:32:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}要不我去吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Should I do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.85,1:32:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.60,1:32:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是律师所谓的"相关方"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're what the lawyers call "an interested party."
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.81,1:32:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.40,1:32:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是说  我们可以跟达格利什小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You mean we'd be up there on the screen
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.07,1:32:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}和德克斯特先生一起上大银幕吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}with Miss Dalgleish and Mr. Dexter?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.86,1:32:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你确定吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.57,1:32:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-就是这样  -我乐意\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- That's exactly what I mean. - Well, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.70,1:32:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}卡森先生也会乐意的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mm, so will Mr. Carson.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.91,1:32:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫斯利先生也会想加入的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mr. Molesley will want to join in.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.49,1:32:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-你需要多少人  -十个人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- How many do you need? - Uh, we need ten.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.25,1:32:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}丹可小姐  你想去吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Miss Denker, are you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.50,1:32:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当然不要\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Certainly not.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.67,1:32:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还要照顾老夫人呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I want to keep an eye on Her Ladyship.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.71,1:32:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-那梅森先生呢  -我可以去问问\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- What about Mr. Mason? - I could always ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.42,1:32:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不  现在就赶紧去农场问他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}No, hurry to the farm and ask him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.50,1:32:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们有适合我们的戏服吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And they've got costumes for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.71,1:32:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们需要时间改尺寸\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, well, they'll need time to fit them,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.88,1:32:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们今天结束前得去一趟楼上服装部\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}so you should go upstairs to wardrobe before the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.55,1:32:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那仆人呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What about servants?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.47,1:32:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谁来服侍我们啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Who's going to wait on us?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.39,1:32:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我在想  可以让艾伯特来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I was thinking we could use Albert.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.77,1:32:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我能为达格利什小姐服务吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Would I be serving Miss Dalgleish?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.64,1:32:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-可以啊  -好啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- I suppose so. - Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.94,1:33:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好了  都回去工作吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Right, let's get back to work, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.06,1:33:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-好了  走吧  -快点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- All right, come on now. - Come along.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.15,1:33:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}拍电影肯定是史上最慢的职业了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Filming must be the slowest occupation known to man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.20,1:33:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}冰川都显得不耐烦了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It makes a glacier look impatient.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.32,1:33:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}罗伯特一定难受死了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose Robert's in hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.66,1:33:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他还指望着等他们回来时一切都结束了呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He was longing for it all to be over by the time they got back.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.62,1:33:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你想  可以缓解他的痛苦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You could ease his pain if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.00,1:33:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们发现了蒙米拉先生的信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We found the letters of Monsieur de Montmirail.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.25,1:33:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但罗伯特仍没有得到他需要的答案\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But Robert still doesn't have the answer he needs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.80,1:33:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不会假装我没听懂\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I won't pretend not to understand you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.01,1:33:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们跟你说小画像的事了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Did they tell you about the miniature?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.09,1:33:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}它有什么意义\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What's its significance?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.76,1:33:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可以拿来吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, could you fetch it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.89,1:33:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在右边下面的抽屉里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's in the bottom right-hand drawer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.81,1:33:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果你打开后面\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If you open it at the back,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.39,1:33:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}会发现他附的那封信\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}you'll find the letter he sent with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.40,1:33:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这么多年了  还在呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's still there after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.44,1:33:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可以读出来吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could you read it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.70,1:33:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"亲爱的维奥莱特  我们错过了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}"Chère Violette, we have missed the chance
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.54,1:33:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}享受完美爱情的机会\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}to know perfect love.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.96,1:34:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但如果你肯改主意  我们还有机会"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But we still can if you would only change your mind."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.13,1:34:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你怎么不直说呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why didn't you just tell us?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.76,1:34:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没什么好说的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}There was nothing to tell.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.76,1:34:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么都没发生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.14,1:34:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}就是被纠缠了好多年\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Apart from years of being pestered.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.47,1:34:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.89,1:34:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}也不是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.06,1:34:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那究竟是怎么回事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.60,1:34:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那之后我再没见过他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I never saw him after that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.27,1:34:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道我会受不了诱惑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I knew I'd have given in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.32,1:34:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果我再经受考验  肯定会犯错\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If I'd been tested again, I would have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.24,1:34:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我当时是个痴情的傻瓜\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was a fool for love in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.49,1:34:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}几年后  我们去了俄国\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A few years later, we went to Russia,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.00,1:34:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我又惹了大麻烦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I got into terrible trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.83,1:34:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}险些吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I nearly did.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.46,1:34:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}跟克拉根亲王  我知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}With Prince Kuragin. Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.38,1:34:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是怎么避免在侯爵身上犯错的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}How did you avoid it with the marquis?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.63,1:34:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我记不得了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't think.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.47,1:34:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他真是我这辈子见过的最有魅力的男人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He was the most attractive man I'd ever met in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.51,1:34:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我才结婚不久\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I hadn't long been married,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.47,1:35:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}肯定是觉得破坏我的婚姻未免太可惜\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and it must have seemed a shame, you know, to spoil that.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.64,1:35:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}真希望你说出来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I wish you'd said all this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.06,1:35:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不希望你觉得我一辈子都过得很违心\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I didn't want you to think my life had been a fraud,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.65,1:35:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为我没有\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}when it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.07,1:35:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我跟罗伯特的父亲挺幸福的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I was happy with Robert's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.57,1:35:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}以英国人的方式足够幸福了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, happy enough in that English way,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.16,1:35:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们什么都不说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}when you never talk about anything
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.79,1:35:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但还是信任彼此\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but you trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.00,1:35:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果克拉根和蒙米拉合体了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}If they'd put Kuragin and Montmirail together,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.04,1:35:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我肯定会堕落成一个荡妇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I would have come out as some sort of scarlet woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.21,1:35:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可不觉得你浪荡\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You don't seem very scarlet to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.76,1:35:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要委托你确保人们不会这么想我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I'm trusting you to make sure that's not how I'm remembered.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.81,1:35:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}下任伯爵就是马修的儿子了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, the next earl will be Matthew's son,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.31,1:35:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我孙子  你的曾孙\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}my grandson, your great-grandson.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.86,1:35:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我会尽力让他珍重你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'll do my best to see he values you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.98,1:35:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道你会的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.15,1:35:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道我可以信任你做正确的事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know I can trust you to do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.70,1:35:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}多谢你这么说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That's very generous of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.41,1:36:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}因为我们有过不少分歧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, because we've had our tussles, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.16,1:36:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}的确是  但我很高兴你来到了唐顿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, it's true, but I'm glad you came to Downton.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.46,1:36:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很多年来  我都没有一个\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd never known anyone whose opinion I could trust,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.09,1:36:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}能相信她总会做出正直判断的人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}you know, to be morally right, not for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.84,1:36:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}自我母亲死后就没有了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, not since my mother died.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.09,1:36:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你肯定好奇我为什么让你整理我的文件\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You must have wondered why I asked you to go through my papers.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.60,1:36:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我是好奇\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I did rather.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.18,1:36:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当我想起很久以前的世界\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When I think about that world of long ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.77,1:36:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当我还是个初次穿裙衬的姑娘\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}when I... I was a girl in my first crinoline...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.78,1:36:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}在那些时刻  我好像\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}...in those moments, I feel
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.57,1:36:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}去了另一个星球\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}as if I've been transported to a different planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.16,1:36:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}的确是这样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And so you have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.99,1:36:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}每个活得够久的人都会有这种感觉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Like every human being who lives long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.54,1:36:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊  我的确活了够久了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I have. Lived long enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.34,1:36:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不是那个意思\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.60,1:37:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}抱歉  但我等不及了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm sorry, but I just couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.85,1:37:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}没事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.02,1:37:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么都没发生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.11,1:37:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是你父亲的儿子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You're your father's son.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.74,1:37:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不能假装这没让我如释重负\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't pretend I'm not relieved.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.95,1:37:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不能假装这没让我觉得受辱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't pretend I'm not insulted.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.16,1:37:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}如果这跟我的出生毫无关系\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Why do you think he gave you the villa
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.04,1:37:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那他为什么要把别墅送你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}if it has nothing to do with my birth?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.66,1:37:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我觉得这跟你的出生很有关系\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I think it had everything to do with your birth.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.12,1:37:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你的出生  让他明白\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}When you were born, it sent a message
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.09,1:37:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他想要的永远都不可能了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}that what he wanted was never going to happen
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.13,1:37:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他该向前看了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and it was time to move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.67,1:37:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他从未像爱您那样爱过他妻子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He never loved his wife as he loved you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.43,1:37:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别墅就证明了这点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}The villa proves that.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.01,1:37:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.93,1:37:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我就不知道了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}...that's not for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.40,1:37:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-嗯  -好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Yeah. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.99,1:38:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看了最后一场戏\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I looked through the final scenes.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.66,1:38:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很不错\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.87,1:38:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你喜欢这样的工作吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Does this kind of work appeal to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.16,1:38:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}为电影写剧本\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}writing plays for the screen?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.96,1:38:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What, you-you mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.13,1:38:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}比如一年四部\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, say, four a year.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.88,1:38:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我会把我看好的书或短篇故事寄给你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd send you the book or short story I was keen on
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.88,1:38:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}上面写好注释和建议\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}with my notes and suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.38,1:38:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}一千块的剧本我给你七百几尼\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Um, I would pay 700 guineas against a thousand.
