Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.94,1:46:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这也包括你未来的家人吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Does that include any future member of your family?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.57,1:47:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当然  因为...\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, yes, of course, becau...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.49,1:47:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}现在还早  所以什么都别说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It's early days, so don't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.91,1:47:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亲爱的  我什么都不会说\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, my darling, I won't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.04,1:47:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我想我可以吻你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I think that I can kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.42,1:47:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}克拉克森医生来了  老爷\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Dr. Clarkson has arrived, milord.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.42,1:47:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我注意到你跟那位帅气的巴伯先生十分亲近\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I notice you're very friendly with the handsome Mr. Barber.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.42,1:47:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别闹\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Don't start.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.47,1:47:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我没惹麻烦  一直乖乖的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've kept myself out of trouble and I've been good.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.89,1:47:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但的确忍得挺辛苦\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}With some difficulty, I might add.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.35,1:47:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}并不是你担心的那样\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It is not what you were dreading.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.14,1:47:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}恶性贫血往往会被误诊为癌症\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Pernicious anemia is often mistaken for cancer.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.60,1:47:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}直到几年前\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And until a few years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:36.19,1:47:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}的确可能会要了你的命\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}it might well have finished you off.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.36,1:47:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但现在有治疗办法了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But there is now treatment.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.62,1:47:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢天谢地\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.49,1:47:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}虽然不会很舒服\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It won't be particularly enjoyable,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.03,1:47:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但你会好起来  你不会死的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}but you will get better and you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.53,1:47:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢  克拉克森医生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, thank you, Dr. Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.74,1:47:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}非常感谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you very, very, very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.66,1:47:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊  谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.54,1:47:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您也进来吃点晚餐吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, you must come in and have some supper.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.67,1:47:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不过今晚上挺将就的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But it's very much catch-as-catch-can tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.92,1:47:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}仆人们都当了把影星\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}All the servants are film stars now.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.80,1:48:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们大概别指望他们会愿回去当仆人了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I doubt we'll ever get them back behind the green baize door.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.01,1:48:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}老爷\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, milord!
