Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.84,1:48:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}快来啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Please, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.76,1:48:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}医生\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.81,1:48:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}再来一次\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.60,1:48:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}用那个口音\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Talk in that voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.85,1:48:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我只想说  我非常感激\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I just wanna say how grateful I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:16.94,1:48:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们在我需要的时候帮我振作了起来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You both licked me into shape when I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.36,1:48:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.36,1:48:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-那你要去好莱坞了  -为什么不呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- So you'll go to Hollywood now? -  Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.36,1:48:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这里也没有家人值得我留恋\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I've no family to hold me here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.28,1:48:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}而且我现在拍过有声片了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I've done a talkie now,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.24,1:48:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我算是领先一步了  希望是吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}which puts me ahead of the race, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.24,1:48:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别忘了你是谁和你的出身就好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Just don't forget who you are or where you've come from.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.16,1:48:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但也别让它阻碍你\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But don't let it hold you back either.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.41,1:48:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}祝你好运\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And good luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.62,1:48:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}过来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.17,1:48:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}老夫人的状况在急转直下\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Old Lady Grantham's sinking fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.47,1:48:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们都在楼上陪她呢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}They're upstairs with her now.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.05,1:48:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}准备点咖啡或更烈的东西  以防万一\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Get some coffee or something stronger just in case.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.69,1:48:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}查理  你没事吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Charlie, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.48,1:49:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}李尔王怎么说的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What did King Lear say?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.07,1:49:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}"吹啊  大风  吹裂你的脸颊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}"Blow, winds, and crack your cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.57,1:49:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}发作啊  吹啊  激流和狂飙"\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Rage, blow, you cataracts and hurricanoes."
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.24,1:49:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她离开的时刻终于到来了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Has the moment of her leaving come at last?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.29,1:49:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这么一位尊贵的夫人即将离世\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}That so great a lady should go
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.01,1:49:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}家里却有一堆拍电影的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}when the house is full of film people.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.15,1:49:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}莫德\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Maud.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.06,1:49:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你怎么也在\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.36,1:49:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不会相信的  但我会怀念你的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, you won't believe me, but I sh... I shall miss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.57,1:49:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是来确认我快不行了吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Or have you just come to check I'm on the way out?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.66,1:49:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您需要什么吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Is there anything you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.95,1:50:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想要的  亲爱的孩子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Whatever I have wanted, dearest boy,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.67,1:50:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你早就给过我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}you have given me long before now
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.00,1:50:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很多次了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and many times over.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.96,1:50:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亲爱的妈妈  希望我没让您失望\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Dear Mama, I hope I haven't been a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.30,1:50:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}您一向比我聪明多了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You were always so much cleverer than me.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.51,1:50:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}True.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.60,1:50:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我们现在别为了这个闹别扭了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But don't let that come between us now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.60,1:50:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你可比我这辈子善良多了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You are far kinder than I have ever been.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.40,1:50:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}柯拉  我欠你个道歉\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Cora, I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.40,1:50:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我没想到你能撑下来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I didn't think you'd last the course.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.16,1:50:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我知道\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.45,1:50:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但我错了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.74,1:50:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们以前可没听我说过这种话\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, that's something you haven't heard me say until now.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.21,1:50:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这句话值得等待\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It was worth waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.17,1:50:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亲爱的玛丽  还有伊迪丝\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, Mary dear and Edith.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.59,1:50:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你们都是好孙女\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You've been wonderful granddaughters.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.51,1:50:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我离开你们时\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I leave you both
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.59,1:50:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}坚信你们一生都会幸福丰富\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}confident that your lives will be happy and fruitful.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.60,1:51:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}奶奶\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.23,1:51:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}亲爱的奶奶\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Darling Granny.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.31,1:51:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这样就够了吧\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now, that must be enough
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.36,1:51:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不然我要像那些把行李搬上车\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}or I shall be like one of those guests who
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.19,1:51:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}却不肯走的客人了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}pack the car and never leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.49,1:51:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}夫人\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mila-- Milady...
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.82,1:51:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}别吵吵了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Stop that noise.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:17.20,1:51:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我都听不到自己死去了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't hear myself die.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.93,1:53:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这个也端过去\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Take that as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:27.02,1:54:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢  贝茨\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you, Bates.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.85,1:54:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这对我们来说是不寻常的日子\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}A strange day for you and me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.86,1:54:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们终于成了孤儿\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We're orphans at last.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.07,1:54:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-早上好  -早上好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Good morning. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.29,1:54:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.37,1:54:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你能来她会很高兴的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She'd be so pleased you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:56.09,1:54:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我还记得我第一次真切地看到她  小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can remember the first time I really saw her, milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.46,1:55:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}近距离看她\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, close up, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:01.97,1:55:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我当时刚从门童升了职\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd just been promoted from hallboy,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:04.09,1:55:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我跟当时的管家蒙乔伊先生在餐厅里\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I was in the dining room with the old butler then, Mr. Mountjoy.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.77,1:55:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我一直很怕他\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I'd been terrified of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.93,1:55:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但她向我们走了过来\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But then she walked towards us.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.10,1:55:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她当时在气什么事\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She was angry about something, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:16.19,1:55:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我看到他都颤抖了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I could see him tremble.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.94,1:55:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我永远没忘记那一幕\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I never forgot that.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.11,1:55:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}那之后我就再不怕他了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I was never afraid of him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.91,1:55:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你是我们家族历史的一部分\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You belong to our history.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.87,1:55:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}事实上  或许这段历史还没结束\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In fact, I wonder if your part is quite done.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.95,1:55:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你愿意考虑回来工作吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Would you ever consider coming back?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:32.71,1:55:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}至少再工作一阵\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}For a bit longer anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.00,1:55:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}什么意思  小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Milady?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.25,1:55:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}巴罗要走了  我不能一个人调教一个新管家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Barrow is leaving, and I can't break in a new butler alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.67,1:55:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}可以让安德鲁在你的指导下准备接替你吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could Andrew be your steady hand while you train him up to succeed you?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.55,1:55:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你觉得他能行吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Could he manage that, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.09,1:55:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}当然行\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, certainly.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.97,1:55:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}假以时日的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}In time.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.98,1:55:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}老夫人的胸针\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Her Ladyship's brooch.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:54.44,1:55:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}唐顿的火炬被传给您了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}So now the Downton torch has passed to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.90,1:56:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是传给老爷\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}To His Lordship.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.94,1:56:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}但如果我也要接过火炬  我要尽量骄傲地举起它\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}But if I'm to carry it, too, I shall try to do so with pride.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.91,1:56:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我不能假装我没感到有些害怕\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can't pretend I'm not a little frightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.83,1:56:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你不必害怕\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Oh, you have no need to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.50,1:56:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你有这个力量\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You have the strength for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.33,1:56:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Do I?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.37,1:56:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我有时会怀疑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Sometimes I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.08,1:56:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我可不怀疑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well, I don't wonder.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.34,1:56:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}毫不怀疑\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Not for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.63,1:56:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不管重不重要  你永远可以指望我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And you can always count on me, if that means anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.55,1:56:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这对我意义非凡\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}It means a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.35,1:56:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这你是知道的\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}And I think you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.31,1:56:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我要单独待会儿再出发\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Now I just need a moment before we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:39.40,1:56:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是  小姐\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Milady.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.17,1:57:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她说了什么\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What did she have to say?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.67,1:57:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她希望我回来工作\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She wants me back in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.88,1:57:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}做管家\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}As butler.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.67,1:57:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Does she indeed?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.89,1:57:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我们该走了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}We ought to move off.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.01,1:57:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢你组织了一切\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thanks for organizing this.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:14.06,1:57:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}她留下了事无巨细的指示\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}She left instructions down to the tiniest detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.89,1:57:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}不难想象\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.14,1:57:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你将来还要安葬我\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}You'll be burying me one day,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.69,1:57:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}很高兴到时一切都会妥妥当当\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}and I'm glad to see it'll be done well.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:22.11,1:57:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}我想重要的是\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}I suppose the point is
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.36,1:57:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}卡劳利家的人来来去去  但家族会一直传承\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}individual Crawleys come and go, but the family lives on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.24,1:57:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}妈妈知道也相信这一点\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Mama knew that and believed in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.61,1:57:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}是啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Didn't she just.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.93,1:58:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这边走  我们进去了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}This way now. We shall go inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.00,1:59:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.29,1:59:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他们来了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.30,1:59:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好可爱\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Adorable.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.63,1:59:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.43,1:59:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-恭喜  -谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.05,1:59:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}太棒了\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.47,2:00:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你累吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Are you exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.39,2:00:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}茜玻  你还好吗\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Sybbie, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.40,2:00:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}-恭喜  -谢谢\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}- Congratulations. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:14.07,2:00:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}好漂亮的宝宝\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}What a bonny baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:15.45,2:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}他真帅气\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}He's very handsome.
