Dialogue: 0,2:00:19.24,2:00:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}你好\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.45,2:00:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn幼圆\仿宋20\b1}这是谁啊\N{\c&H009CFF&\fn微软雅黑\仿宋 18}Who's this?

